metadata.name: Tissueblue 0 0125 mg 0 5mL Injection solution
metadata.composition: 0 0125 mg 0 5mL Ebola Zaire vaccine live attenuated

clinical_particulars.therapeutic_indications: Ebola Zaire vaccine is indicated for active immunization of individuals 18 years of age or older to protect against Ebola Virus Disease EVD caused by _Zaire Ebolavirus_ L10857

contraindications.disease: There is limited information on the overdose and LD sub 50 sub of Ebola Zaire vaccine
contraindications.pharmacodynamics: Ebola Zaire vaccine protects against the Ebola virus infection and disease by introducing a protein produced by the _Zaire ebolavirus_ and initiating the body s normal immune responses against the virus In clinical trials consisting of subjects receiving the Ebola virus vaccine the vaccine virus RNA was detected in the plasma samples of most subjects within the first week after intramuscular injection L10854
